headline: Jacobs Announces Multi-Year Growth Strategy at 2025 Investor Day
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) will outline its multi-year growth strategy and set out its long-term financial framework at its 2025 Investor Day February 18, 2025. The company's strategy, Challenge Accepted, accelerates Jacobs' transformation to a more focused business positioned to drive profitable growth and deliver market-leading infrastructure, water, life sciences and advanced manufacturing solutions.
